                                                        "At \u003cstrong\u003eLacostaHaus\u003c/strong\u003e, we are pleased to present this outstanding 4-star superior hotel project in the historic 16th-century \u003cem\u003eMas Candell\u003c/em\u003e farmhouse, recognised as part of Catalonia\u0027s cultural heritage.",
                                                        "This remarkable property sits on a \u003cstrong\u003e10,680 m²\u003c/strong\u003e plot, less than 2 kilometres from the beautiful beaches of Platja d’Aro and the lively town centre, with restaurants, shops and leisure activities. It is also close to the marina and several renowned golf courses.",
