                                                        "The farmhouse will be the heart of the hotel, with a charming reception and lounge area, \u003cstrong\u003e11 suites\u003c/strong\u003e and \u003cstrong\u003e6 superior rooms\u003c/strong\u003e, as well as a restaurant for \u003cstrong\u003e50 diners\u003c/strong\u003e with its own kitchen. Guests will enjoy two spacious terraces: one for \u003cstrong\u003e100 people\u003c/strong\u003e and another with a \u003cstrong\u003e200 m² chill-out area\u003c/strong\u003e.",
                                                        "Another part of the hotel will consist of \u003cstrong\u003e14 individual family bungalows\u003c/strong\u003e, each with its own entrance and spacious terraces. The bungalows will be located next to a large green area with mature trees that provide shade and a relaxing atmosphere.",
